      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing system. Power is managed by a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to address floor pan fatigue, and the suspension retains its factory-spec MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry for exceptional lateral grip. This example is a mechanically sound, well-maintained machine that offers the visceral, analog feedback expected of the M-division's hallmark naturally aspirated era.",
