    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 530i finished in Sophisto Grey Metallic with a Black Dakota Leather interior. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior retains a deep, high-gloss shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a faint 2-inch scratch on the lower rear bumper consistent with city parking. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment. The leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light bolster wear on the driver's side. Every electronic feature\u2014including the iDrive infotainment system, heated seats, and sunroof\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is sound; it has a full service history with the most recent oil service and brake fluid flush completed just 1,500 miles ago. The 2.0L turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, and the 8-speed transmission shifts flawlessly. This is a complete package for someone seeking luxury and performance without the showroom price tag. Includes two keys and all original manuals.",
